    "summary": "__NOTOC__ Crushbone is the home of the Crushbone clan of orcs. It is located directly to the north of the wood elf city of Kelethin, and is the major thorn in the sides of all the inhabitants of Faydwer. Once you enter Crushbone there are orcs everywhere and there are almost always trains because of the close proximity of the orc spawns. There are also many high levels that will power level lower level groups. Crushbone can be entered cautiously at level 6 and can bring you to about level 15 if you are able to hold down the throne room or legionnaires comfortably.",
