    "pageTitle": "Erud's Crossing",
    "era": "Classic",
    "summary": "The trade routes from here to Odus are busy and prosperous, but can also be very dangerous. -Captain Rohand Erud's Crossing is the name of the zone which the ferry from Qeynos to Erudin passes through, and it marks the path that Erud himself travelled on his way to the island of Odus centuries ago. Erud's Crossing's only feature is an island that marks the halfway point of the trip, and it is a most unique island, with its own ecosystem of unique creatures.",
