      "13. \"Boil's Lair\" with Cauldronboil who drops Sharkjaw Cutlass (Common) and Kedgemail Gauntlets (Rare)",
      "14. \"Frenzied Room\" with Frenzied Cauldron Shark who drops Shark Tooth (Common) and Abalone Gorget (Rare)",
