      "3. A skeletal cook is a static spawn who drops Shield of Kurn (Uncommon) who does not agro to anyone. You can hand a A Glowing Skull to the cook to recieve The Skull of Torture in return. A Wandering fingered skeleton spawns nearby who drops various size Skeleton Fingers, he is not the same spawn as the cook!! Killing the cook does not make the fingered skeleton appear. Only the wandering mobs in the hallway are PH for the fingered skeleton.",
      "4. Bargynn who drops Bargynn's Torch (Common) and Bargynn's Digger (Common)"
