    "summary": "The Feerrott is the dark swampy home of the ogres and lizard men of Antonica. The ogres live in a cave system at the edge of the swamp, while the lizard men have established camps scattered throughout. It is also the home of the ancient ruined temple of Cazic-Thule. Note: No Tae Ew mobs are in The Feerrott, they are in Cazic Thule on p99.",
